<ServiceHero
  eyebrow="Failure mode · Real Crack vs Etching · Replacement Only · Insurance"
  title="Cooktop Glass Cracked, Glass-Ceramic Surface"
  subtitle="Residential glass cooktops across LA, OC, Ventura, Riverside. Worth $89 to confirm real crack vs cookware drag etching. Replacement only on confirmed cracks. (424) 325-0520"
