        <tr><td>Schott Ceran lead time (premium brands)</td><td>4 to 6 weeks typical</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Insurance damage documentation</td><td>Included with diagnostic</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Warranty</td><td>90 days parts and labor</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="price-note">Residential $89 diagnostic, applied toward repair. About 20% of "cracked cooktop" calls resolve at diagnostic with polishing test (no parts).</p>
  </div>
</section>

